    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 15</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You attempt to remove a single seal of Rank 5 or lower from the target, of which you must be aware. You make a Chakra Control check (DC 15), which is increased by the complexity rating of the technique that made the seal: E (+0), D (+1), C (+3), B (+5), A (+7), S (+10) or SS (+15).<br><br>Removing a seal requires one person using this technique simultaneously per seal slot it occupies on the target's body.</p>\n\n\n\n",
